a. and the fifth _ one more. that's the last one
the last count charges a conspiracy to defraud the internal revenue service by using a tax-exempt foundation, the national endowment for the preservation of liberty, to _ to generate funds for the contras
but would you just _ i can't figure it out what you want me to do
