the news therefore provided an optimistic tone to stock trading and substantiated other evidence that the economy is growing despite fears of a slowdown raised by the october crash
i think the trade number was just what everybody liked,'' said philip c. puccio, manager of institutional trading at dillon, read &amp; co. in new york. ``it brought a sigh of relief.''
